oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ronnie Reno Studio Recordings
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Ronnie Reno (musician). The recording features Ronnie Reno performing: "If You Really Go," "Agitatin' My Mind," "My Love is Love," "Kentucky Serenade," "The Thrill of the Chase," "Kentucky Gold," "Boogie Grass Saturday Night," "Dobro Man," "I've Seen That Horse Run," "My Baby Sure Ain't Home," "Constantly in Love." Recordings are from a variety of unidentified dates.
